---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base>
  <section class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-12 dark:prose-invert">
    <h1>About Waypoint Digital Library</h1>
    <p>Waypoint Digital Library is a proof-of-concept for building sustainable, high-quality digital library experiences on a static stack. The project leverages Astro, Tailwind CSS, and GitHub Actions to orchestrate ingest, publishing, and deployment.</p>
    <p>All works are edited and reviewed according to our quality rubric. Metadata follows library-informed best practices with JSON-LD enrichment for discoverability.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
